Blocks.Text: In the SF track, we benchmark the representative CNN-based and vision transformer-based pose
estimation methods, including SimpleBaseline, HRNet, HRFormer, and ViTPose.
We set up three settings to benchmark their performance, including using network weights pre-trained on
the ImageNet-IK dataset, the MS COCO human pose estimation dataset, and the AP-10K dataset,
